			"fieldtype": "Password",
			"label": "USB Token PIN",
			"reqd": 1
		},
		{
			"depends_on": "eval:doc.eta_einvoice_enabled && doc.eta_signer_mode==\"signing_agent\"",
			"description": "Chilkat UnlockBundle key for v10 (e.g. HALA4A.CBX082025_…). Sent once to the Windows agent via sign_session (like PIN). Optional if you set CHILKAT_UNLOCK_CODE or chilkat_config.json on the PC.",
